  + [source_type] is dictated refinement
  + [source_scope] is C:\Project\Pinky\.sop narrative, subject inquiry, and file inspection flow
  + [raw_direction] is "so then the narrative layer should lead the subject inquiry layer to find what files to inspect to follow a given subject"
  + [interpreted_need] is define a SubjectInquiry layer that receives a narrative subject, queries the narrative subject file index, builds an inspection queue, and then routes selected file surfaces into deeper inquiry lookup
